{"tid":796113,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Alipay HK 將推出「易乘碼」 QR CODE 香港交通支付　傳專線小巴首先開通","createTime":"2018-08-27T13:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T06:24:47.000Z","uid":137335,"like":12,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"cb3c32e4230a631ed4beb8f6812e597318dc3c46","tid":796113,"uid":137335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"AlipayHK 在最新的 BETA 版中無意中洩露了將支援掃描二維碼支付車資，消息指新服務將率先應用於專線小巴，有望日後擴展至其他交通工具。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAlipayHK 的新功能名為「易乘碼」，在有關頁面寫明「支援離線使用，先乘車後付款」，並且「率先支持部份專線小巴」。有網民擔心，QR Code 支付車資會減慢付款速度，因為要對準角度及有足夠亮度才可進行掃描，不像八達通一樣快。亦有網民表示，收到銀行通知，在 9 月 17 日更改服務條款，原因是銀行有意推出各大付款工具互通及銀行戶口互通服務，還可以用國際標準二維碼進行交易。但不少網民認為，用二維碼支付是「科技倒退」的象徵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/08/27/rumourssayalipayisgoingtolaunchqrcodescanningforpayingtransportationfee/life-tech/epayment/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2Frumourssayalipayisgoingtolaunchqrcodescanningforpayingtransportationfee%2Flife-tech%2Fepayment%2F&d=r9Q0H30ZMVfHfo%2FzEKTzOZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=1b3a99b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/08/27/rumourssayalipayisgoingtolaunchqrcodescanningforpayingtransportationfee/life-tech/epayment/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你個八達通，明明將卡加埋入Apple pay同Google pay已經無撚敵，比個支那寶整個交通payment仲柒下柒下咁，未入到你地八達通有股分嘅公共交通公司就唔撚理架嗱"},{"pid":"81926be5c9caf15a6a75239dfe77be1eecefc0a8","tid":796113,"uid":23872,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T13:45:53.000Z","msg":"哇正啊 香港正式進入智慧城市 同支拿接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c80273871bf09826e390b7d77e56e0d